                                                    <p style="margin-bottom: 1em; margin:0; -ms-text-size-adjust:100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust:100%; mso-line-height-rule:exactly; text-align:center" align="center"><span style="font-size: 16px;">When we discovered in our recent survey of 200+ marketers that only 16% are using A/B testing to optimize the customer journey we were surprised!</span></p>
                                                    <p style="margin-bottom: 1em; margin:0; -ms-text-size-adjust:100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust:100%; mso-line-height-rule:exactly; text-align:center" align="center">&nbsp;</p>
                                                    <p style="margin-bottom: 1em; margin:0; -ms-text-size-adjust:100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust:100%; mso-line-height-rule:exactly; text-align:center" align="center"><span style="font-size: 16px;">Yes, it has it's challenges, but A/B testing is an essential part of understanding your customer journey and improving it. So <a href="https://resources.yieldify.com/ecommerce-ab-testing/?utm_campaign=A%2FB%20Testing%20ebook&amp;utm_source=hs_email&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=67532649&amp;_hsenc=p2ANqtz-_torQEqq8HqR7GcfgvQzi-ZNLOusUh35K0Y358fz0qRIuo0nV5qzPmS-gO6zJn_O-R9GMX7Gjer6cisW4W_ShD3T7GrQjTtBS_xOk3w1zdQ5diBcg" rel=" noopener" style="-ms-text-size-adjust:100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust:100%; mso-line-height-rule:exactly; color:#0077cc" data-hs-link-id="1" target="_blank">in this guide</a> we're taking you through the why, where, when and how of A/B testing for e-commerce. </span></p>
                                                    <p style="margin-bottom: 1em; margin:0; -ms-text-size-adjust:100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust:100%; mso-line-height-rule:exactly; text-align:center" align="center">&nbsp;</p>
                                                    <p style="margin-bottom: 1em; margin:0; -ms-text-size-adjust:100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust:100%; mso-line-height-rule:exactly; text-align:center" align="center"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><strong>Inside you'll find:</strong></span></p>
                                                    <p style="margin-bottom: 1em; margin:0; -ms-text-size-adjust:100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust:100%; mso-line-height-rule:exactly; text-align:center" align="center"><span style="font-size: 16px;">- The key challenges, and how to overcome them</span></p>
                                                    <p style="margin-bottom: 1em; margin:0; -ms-text-size-adjust:100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust:100%; mso-line-height-rule:exactly; text-align:center" align="center"><span style="font-size: 16px;">- Ideas on what to test with real-life examples</span></p>
                                                    <p style="margin-bottom: 1em; margin:0; -ms-text-size-adjust:100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust:100%; mso-line-height-rule:exactly; text-align:center" align="center"><span style="font-size: 16px;">-Tips on the pitfalls to look out for and avoid</span></p></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>
                                <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-spacing:0 !important; -ms-text-size-adjust:100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust:100%; border-collapse:collapse; mso-table-lspace:0pt; mso-table-rspace:0pt; font-family:Lato, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:1.75; color:#4e4e4e; word-break:break-word"><tbody><tr><td style="border-collapse:collapse; -ms-text-size-adjust:100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust:100%; mso-line-height-rule:exactly; font-family:Lato, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:1.75; color:#4e4e4e; word-break:break-word; padding:10px 20px"><div id="hs_cos_wrapper_module_153968818049642" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module" style="color: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit;" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="module">

                                                <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="border-spacing:0 !important; -ms-text-size-adjust:100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust:100%; border-collapse:collapse; mso-table-lspace:0pt; mso-table-rspace:0pt; font-family:Lato, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:1.75; color:#4e4e4e; word-break:break-word">
